  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nProposing a method (if possible) under the `PanacheBaseEntity ` class and `PanacheRepositoryBase `interface to return a boolean value if an entity by ID exists.\r\n\r\nCurrent logic everytime we check if an entity exists:\r\n\r\n```\r\npublic boolean isPersonExists() {\r\n  Person p = Person.findById(1);\r\n\r\n  return Objects.nonNull(p);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis is always the case whenever trying to check if an entity exist.\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\nAdd a method\r\n\r\n`boolean existsById(Id id);`\r\n\r\nLet me know for any advice/feedback that you have!",
